<p style="Heading 1"><c props="lang:en-GB"></c>1.9.0 Changelog</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Johan Bj√∂rk</p>
<p style="Normal">Convert 21 QNX dialogs to PhAB (Photon Application Builder).</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Besnik Bleta</p>
<p style="Normal">Albanian localisation work.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Francesco Cheratzu</p>
<p style="Normal">Sardinian localisation work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Sardinian dictionary.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Mikey Cooper</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 1921</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Gery Deloge</p>
<p style="Normal">Various BeOS bug fixes.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jeremy Davis</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4774</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Andrew Dunbar</p>
<p style="Normal">Added UTLANG_RTL and UTLANG_VERTICAL to the appropriate languages, to go with Tomas Frydrych's BiDi brackets work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4784</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Hubert Figuiere</p>
<p style="Normal">Deleted the Carbon files from the tree.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Frank Franklin</p>
<p style="Normal">Extensive work on the way properties are attached to tables, allowing sensible inheritance and, potentially, styling and editing.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bumped wv version number.</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed 'Insert an Footnote' to 'Insert a footnote'.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Tomas Frydrych</p>
<p style="Normal">Work towards bug 2742.</p>
<p style="Normal">Implemented direction markers for BiDi text.</p>
<p style="Normal">Implemented font size increase and decrease functions.</p>
<p style="Normal">Many BiDi fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a tag marking language direction.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a method for handling parentheses more intuitively in mixed-direction text.</p>
<p style="Normal">Keybindings for font increase and decrease and for language direction marking.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed drawing of direction markers when show paragraphs is turned on.</p>
<p style="Normal">bug fixes: 2811</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Daniel Glassey</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on cross-compiling on mingw.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Marco Innocenti</p>
<p style="Normal">Italian localisation work.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to dumpstrings.pl to hide commented-out strings.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Egmont Koblingen</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4782</p>
<p style="Heading 2">William Lachance</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4894</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Dom Lachowicz</p>
<p style="Normal">Removed the menu bar from the Nautilus view.</p>
<p style="Normal">Upgraded the OAF server file.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a race condition which was crashing Abi on launch in gdb.</p>
<p style="Normal">Implemented style locking, which allows you to forbid formatting alterations other than by setting the style.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 1427, 4740, 4741, 4753, 4755, 4891</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jordi Mas</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 Format Table dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Centered the Win32 bullets and numbering and headers/footers dialog boxes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a memory leak in merge cells.</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed combo boxes to radio buttons in the Win32 page number dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Format Footnotes dialog for Win32.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 build fix.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixes to Win32 Format Table dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4651, 4742 (partial), 4793, 4885</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Marc Maurer</p>
<p style="Normal">Gladification of Format Table dialog.</p>
<p style="Normal">Hacked the WordPerfect importer to import OLE wrapped WordPerfect documents.</p>
<p style="Normal">Enabled hinting in the Field Dialog tree views.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Michael Pritchett</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 build fixes arising from Martin Sevior's fix of bug 4717.</p>
<p style="Normal">Win32 layout fixes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 4832</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Martin Sevior</p>
<p style="Normal">Changed AbiWidget:: to AbiWidget-- in property names to avoid confusion due to automatic bonobo conversions.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed lots of bugs and crashes concerning endnotes and tables, and speeded up typing and editing in tables and in docs with footnotes.</p>
<p style="Normal">Made AbiWord function as a Nautilus view.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a gtk-only compile error.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a crash on right-click in bonobo.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed regressions from his commits.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added code to only breaksections if the height of the formatted paragraph changes, which significantly speeds up typing near the beginning of big documents.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix the backspace bug.</p>
<p style="Normal">Disabled a number of table functions which will not be finished before 2.0.</p>
<p style="Normal">Fixed a number of problems with cell selections and clearing.</p>
<p style="Normal">Added a UI description for the nautilus view.</p>
<p style="Normal">Select cell/row/table now work from the menu.</p>
<p style="Normal">Work on the nautilus view.</p>
<p style="Normal">Bug fixes: 3324, 4400, 4546, 4756, 4760, 4717, 4795, 4798, 4799, 4811, 4849, 4855, 4856</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Valentine Sinitsyn</p>
<p style="Normal">Fix to Russian strings file.</p>
<p style="Normal">Build fixes for using mingw on Win32. (Mingw being free software, this means that anyone can now compile on Win32.)</p>
<p style="Normal">Patch to allow 'make distribution' on Win32 using mingw.</p>
<p style="Heading 2">Jesper Skov</p>
<p style="Normal">Big fixes: 3926, 4812</p>
</section>
